#### Keyboard Controls
| Key | Action |
|-----|--------|
| W/↑ | Move forward |
| S/↓ | Move backward |
| A/← | Rotate left |
| D/→ | Rotate right |
| E | Interact / Open door |
| C | Open Codex (policy card viewer) |
| ESC | Pause menu |
| TAB | Toggle minimap |
